survey_response.review_text: I have been consulting Dr.Manjula Raghuveer since 2014 during my conception issues, doctor helped me in referring to fertility specialist. Am conceived nw fr 2nd time, an consulting the same doctor fr prenatal checkups and will have my 2nd baby delivered by her. Pretty much happy with the service. Thanks a lot.....

I was suffering from  dysmennorrhoea from the past ten years and I visited Dr Manjula Raghuveer at cloudnine. I was very happy with madam as she came as a saving grace and solved this nerve wracking issue I've been suffering from a long time. Thank you so much madam* *** *** *** ****

Am really impressed regarding the Doctor guidance and i saw my mother in her approach and having said the ambiance , doctor friendliness was the key elements to highlight and a very tenured and experienced Doctor, and Best Regards to Dr Manjula Raghuveer for her services rendered in Cloud9 which should be remembered and noted in books.

She performed my c section and the incision was perfection, which made my recovery very smooth and quick. She definitely will be my Gynaec for life.

As soon as she see the couple the husband will be her Son and the Wife is her Daughter in Law.  That’s the first time you get mistaken of considering her as Motherly lady. *** **** * ******** ** ******* **** ******* While we visited her for the first time on pregnancy success rate was bad the immediate process suggested was for IUI procedure.

She literally yelled at my wife as it was evident that she could accept the pregnancy confirmation naturally happening which was against her plan. Although we proceeded for consultation in hospital and the medication prescribed was for constipation and computing ***** *** ***** * ******* *** ** *****
